		{
			"type": "action",
			"name": "Appear And Disappear",
			"system": {
				"actionType": {
					"value": "passive"
				},
				"description": {
					"value": "<p>The unexpected savior is @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.conditionitems.Item.zJxUflt9np0q4yML]{Invisible} at all times. While invisible, it doesn’t take any actions, it just observes the creature it is ordered to save. The unexpected savior can appear at @Check[will] and immediately take its turn before the creature it was ordered to save, and it disappears when its duty is complete (such as healing the protected creature, or removing an harmful spell upon the protected creature or similar) or when its slain.</p>",
